<br>
I invited you here to make me feel better and instead you make me feel even worse than before! And I hope you realize that this is a serious problem. Its sort of funny though how this is your realm and yet you let this slip by Mr. &quot;I-Know-Everything&quot;. Maybe Poseidon and Hectate had a point after all. <br>
<br>
::She then looks at Hephaestus with tears washing down her cheeks:: See what happens when perverted uncles marry their nieces?!<br>
<br>
::The physician who was standing by the door walked up to Hades and bowed slightly::<br>
<br>
Please my lord, she is saying things that she would not normally say, it is the medicine she is given that talks.<br>
<br>
::Persephone picks up a small pillow &amp; hurls it over the physician's head barely missing him. With heavy tears streaming her face, she points a dainty finger at the door and she screams at Hades the same way she did her first day there::<br>
<br>
Get out! <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. Faithful wife to Hades... Princess Goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A> at: 5/9/03 9:11:43 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 47<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/9/03 2:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=64>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Suprised!</span><hr size=1> ::Hephaestus' eyes widened a bit as Persephone began screaming at Hades. He was a bit suprised by this, he did not expect this. He patted her on her hand to try and comfort her, but he figured it was not the time for it now:: <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A> at: 5/9/03 2:45:17 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixlordhadesxi>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 249<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/9/03 2:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=65>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Angry</span><hr size=1> ::Hades eyes narrowed, probably at the same time Hephaestus' eyes widened. It was an extreme rarity that he got upset at Persephone. He was PISSED. A purple hue started glowing from his narrowed eyes as he looked at Persephone::<br>
<br>
&quot;Fine!&quot;<br>
<br>
::He turned around and walked towards the door. Without turning around he spoke up::<br>
<br>
&quot;Hephaestus, come!&quot;<br>
<br>
::His voice was harsh, his tone was cold. Colder than usual. He walked through his palace, in what seemed straight and determined. He didn't look around as he might sometimes. He climbed on his chariot, and awaited Hephaestus.::<br>
<br>
::Once they both got on, his chariot took off quicker than anyone had really ever seen it. He rode through Tartarus and exited the front gates. The chariot emerged from the slit ground in front of Mt. Aetna::<br>
<br>
&quot;Your payment is inside your workshop.&quot;  ::Those were the only words spoken by Hades the entire trip::<br>
<br>
::He stayed on his chariot and awaited for Hephaestus to dismount. Once he did, he took off like a bat out of hell back into the ground. THe ground sealing up behind him as if it had never been disturbed. His eyes were still glowing purple and were still narrowed:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 206<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/9/03 4:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=66>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.aishwarya-rai.com/tradi/tash16.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> awaiting</span><hr size=1> ::Persephone calms down a little as she feels Hephaestus' big hand soothe hers. As Hephaestus leaves, she drops her mouth open in horror and distress. After they leave, she breaks down into hard sobs. Looking up sternly she crawls out of bed, making her way into the room where Hades would arrive. She wasn't going to make this easy for him at all, not by a long shot:: <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. Faithful wife to Hades... Princess Goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/9/03 5:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=67>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Back in Aetna</span><hr size=1> ::Hephaestus did 