<br>
::Within moments one of his servant Shades appeared behind him. Hades turned to him and read his his mind. He knew then what had happened to Persephone. He stood up in Anger and vanished in a shadow::<br>
<br>
::Moments later he appeared out of Persephone's own shadow. He looked down at her and shook his head, as the room started getting dark and cold the way the area around the River Styx had. He then picked her up in his arms and placed her on the bed::<br>
